criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Healthy, normal glucose tolerance test, normal blood pressure, no family history of
             diabetes or other metabolic history;

          -  Aged between 18 and 25;

          -  Normal body weight and waist circumference, body mass index (BMI) between 18.5 and
             23.9kg/m2;

          -  No carbohydrate intolerance.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Those with abnormal glucose tolerance, overweight or obese, or lactose or carbohydrate
             intolerance were excluded.
